::Hot Rod::

He did not get a response from Feline. He then saw missiles.
He avoided one, but the second hit the ground in front of him. He flew
into the air, do to the shockwave. Then he came down with a thud. The
first thing he did was open a link to Feline.
"Damn it, talk to me! Search your memory banks. Maybe the Alliance
didn't erase all of it. Maybe there is one memory in there. Something
that will tell you what we shared together. Please! I love you!"
He fired a missile at Sharpedge.
